No. 552. The Chicago, Burlington & Quincy Railway Company, Petitioner, v. The United States. January 27, 1908. Mr. 0. M-i Spencer and Mr. O. H. Dean for petitioner. The Attorney General, The Solicitor General and Mr. Assistant to the Attorney General Purdy for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit granted.
